  "body": "The amount of notary balance is missing from the notary struct in SMC. We should add it to track the balance of deposit amount since there will be slashing condition for the notaries.\r\n\r\nWhat to fix:\r\n1. Notary struct should track notary deposit balance\r\n2. When releasing notary, send current balance instead constant `NOTARY_DEPOSIT`\r\n\r\nA similar [issue](https://github.com/ethereum/sharding/issues/80) was opened from py-evm ",
